Module chav1961.purelib
Package chav1961.purelib.basic

Class AsmScriptEngineFactory

java.lang.Object
chav1961.purelib.basic.AbstractScriptEngineFactory
chav1961.purelib.basic.AsmScriptEngineFactory
All Implemented Interfaces:
javax.script.ScriptEngineFactory
public class AsmScriptEngineFactory
extends AbstractScriptEngineFactory

This class implements ScriptEngineFactory functionality for the Java Byte code Macro Assembler (see AsmWriter). This class is an SPI service and can be accessed via the ScriptEngineManager functionality. Language name for the ScriptEngineManager is "javaasm" or "jasm". To execute compiled assembler immediately, it need contains a public static Object main(Bindings,String[]) method in it. String[] parameters are exactly BasicScriptEngineController.execute(String...) parameters. Using this class thru ScriptEngine.eval(String) method, this String[] parameters are exactly new String[0].

Since:
0.0.2
Author:
Alexander Chernomyrdin aka chav1961
See Also:
ScriptEngineManager, ScriptEngineFactory, ScriptEngine, BasicScriptEngineController, AsmWriter, JUnit tests
